^-{ ^*BDeal of the Week 205 - August 14, 2000^*N }
^-
The ACBL Summer North American Championships are currently taking place in Anaheim, California. Full coverage of this tournament, including ^*BOnline Vugraph^*N, is available through these web sites:

|cs|1|at|^-{ ^*Bwww.acbl.org^*N }

|cs|2|at|{ ^*Bwww.e-bridgemaster.com^*N }
